data.description: Gorgeous home on a sprawling 5 ACRE lot. Low taxes. Completely updated and meticulously maintained. Step inside to an open concept layout that has been tastefully decorated. With 2 living spaces. this creates an ideal setting for large gatherings and entertaining, There is plenty of cabinet space in this large, open kitchen. There is 1 bedroom on the main level and 3 are on the upper level. All of the bedrooms are of generous size. The main bedroom has it's own bath with modern fixtures and finishes and a huge walk in closet.. There is a 24x40 Pole Barn/Garage, with lots of room for storage, hobbies, or a workshop. It's a warm and inviting home. Next summer, grab some iced tea and sit under the wrap around porch. Security system and tv's that are used for the security system stay.Don't miss out on your opportunity to make this remarkable residence your own.
